OL,3,CFootage shows rescue of surfer caught
OL,4,Cin powerful rip current
OL,6,FA surfer was left stranded in choppy
OL,7,Fwaters and gale force winds after
OL,8,Fgetting dragged out to sea by a
OL,9,Fpowerful rip current.
OL,11,FBen Fraser, 30, was saved by Porthcawl
OL,12,FRNLI after a member of the public
OL,13,Fwalking their dog spotted him waving
OL,14,Fin distress.
OL,16,FFootage shows the dramatic rescue of
OL,17,FMr Fraser who has 15 years of surfing
OL,18,Fexperience but said he was not
OL,19,Ffamiliar with the strength of the rip
OL,20,Fcurrent and thought he would be able
OL,21,Fto paddle to safety.
