OL,6,FHowever, he found himself being pulled
OL,7,Feven further out in severe weather
OL,8,Fconditions and signalled for help.
OL,10,FHe was then spotted by the dog walker,
OL,11,Fwho made a 999 call to the coastguard.
OL,13,FHe said: "I attempted to get onto the
OL,14,Frocks at the cliffs, but soon realised
OL,15,Fit was too dangerous.
