OL,3,CFootage shows rescue of surfer caught
OL,4,Cin powerful rip current
OL,6,F"Although I felt pretty calm, I knew I
OL,7,Fcouldn't get back to the beach myself
OL,8,Fand that the light was fading fast,
OL,9,Fwhich might have made it harder for
OL,10,Fpeople to spot me or for the lifeboat
OL,11,Fto find me.
OL,13,F"I want to say a huge thank you to the
OL,14,Flady that saw me wave and called 999
OL,15,Ffor the Coastguard, her quick thinking
OL,16,Fmeant the lifeboat reached me before
OL,17,Fit was dark."
