OL,3,CFootage shows rescue of surfer caught
OL,4,Cin powerful rip current
OL,6,FThe lifeboat was launched shortly
OL,7,Fafter 7.30pm on September 10 and Mr
OL,8,FFraser was located off Hutchwns Point,
OL,9,Fhaving drifted over half a mile away
OL,10,Ffrom the main bay.
OL,12,FGareth Collins, of Porthcawl RNLI,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Despite the strong winds
OL,14,Fgusting to force 7/8 and rough seas,
OL,15,Fwe were able to get on scene quickly
OL,16,Fand soon spotted Ben off Hutchwns
OL,17,FPoint.
